you also exposed skills.

77
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,560
You feigned a limp deliberately,

78
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:21,240
but the habits from years
of learning cannot be hidden.

79
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:24,240
However, at that time,
I merely thought you were secretive.

80
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:27,400
What made me suspicious of you was
what I discovered at Mr. Wang's house.

81
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:30,400
