on the ground at the doorway.

82
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:33,280
It indicates that the culprit
is a master of the ghost step.

83
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,640
At the same time, I noticed

84
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:36,680
