in the investigation.

94
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,840
(Bai Feng)
Although you concealed it,

95
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:57,440
(Bai Feng)
yet the style of the brush

96
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:59,680
was still similar to
the handwriting in Obscure Market.

97
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:03,760
Yes, you are right.

98
